Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.24,0:01:14.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.06,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:29.30,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:34.28,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:41.47,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:46.30,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.32,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的圣诞礼物是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 绝对要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要 提前一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和老妈去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是去不了东京迪斯尼乐园了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节就在旭川公园玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天要一直和你一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一起度过是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外宿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是牵着手睡觉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想的话 我就承诺什么也不做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啦 又没有那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱总会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈 我想预支零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和女友一起过圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是高中生一天该花掉的钱数啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我也要拿出这些钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会答应的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有交换条件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 跟你去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你赎罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的话我不想你那样勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 我想度过一个你会开心的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算分开一年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起这个圣诞节也会重新振奋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明说不相信回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我真不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你刚才说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我就说不去温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么 我没听懂你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我确实明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕特别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我知道和你在一起的时间已经不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因此我才想像平时一样度过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.39,0:04:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算特别 也不是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是应该硬带你去温泉旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 不肯死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好今天像平时一样过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说还不是和平时不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看东方的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入12月 东方的天空就会有很多冬季星座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 暖呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 要拍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常这种时候会拍么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视剧最后一集之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍完不就是女友满脸笑容的美满结局么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是电视剧啊动画什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我要按确定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这表情怎么这么怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 挺可爱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的大头贴总是把你拍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友 是个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 在我告诉你过去的伤痛时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起拍大头贴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我自己也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个我最讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然变得这么让我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傻瓜也许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们第一次拍的大头贴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还有些笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人 还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天特意带来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了东京 多从那边发些照片来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿校服的样子之类 其他的也要多些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使分开 联络也很方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音也能听见 脸也能看见 还能发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不能常打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家经济好像有点紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过每周会打一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多帮帮你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应考没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会只让我妈费劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 脸上粘东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年后一定在东京相见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我不会喜欢上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过了奈奈的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心意我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你等我也会荒废时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊 都说了先不用回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说今后只喜欢他一个么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年后也是 五年后也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会清楚以后的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失信过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃过一次矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我说想保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我 这次就想保护矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我要去东京上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不是说上本地的公立校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢乡下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丢下我一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么要去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去就去吧这种话我说不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京有我的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要的追求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 你丑到一定程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜哭过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨起来就成了这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这样哪能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买冰袋来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先托付在老家的婆婆那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看情况 要能带去东京的公寓我也想带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 住址
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎 不是东京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校在东京啊 到涩谷也就30分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 水口 高桥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正 正在厕所 再过会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大便？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大便大便 好慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她吃啥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的再不回来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家没那么富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假春假都不回来么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 这种日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能消肿么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野没找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 帮你蒙混过关了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢小水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见面也许真要上大学了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已经没问题了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你下了很大决心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我还是会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有多后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是又在重复同样的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是问我想去么 当然是不想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是问分开也没关系么 怎么会没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是要求自己的女人在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还和自己说好不再让视线离开她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在的时间 我不会出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我怎么这么天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是傻瓜吗傻瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 不公平我也不会舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有不得不去的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你要是大意 真的让目光离开高桥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 我会一口气抢走她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的比试在那边进行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我啊 一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么从心底松了口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你要是跟她一起念书一起去图书馆我受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那倒是会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那夏日祭典也会一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 这不是着实出手了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊 是作为朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会察言观色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多寂寞 多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了 七美在这里想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野绝不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正负为零
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你非常非常喜欢的人可能已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是非常非常喜欢你的人不是还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正负抵消不就是零了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要觉得你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是零 而是正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你相遇至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是为了和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的确曾经在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱上你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有众多的初次和不可计数的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.77,0:22:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解坚强与软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}确实 我们确实曾在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:22:01.69,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今　君が言いかけた言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:08.27,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指先にそっと降りてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:13.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何も言わなくていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:20.46,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}つないだ指をぎゅっと暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:27.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言葉は言葉だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:35.71,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心半分も伝えないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:44.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切なくて　もどかしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:50.69,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕焼けが二人を包んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:57.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こみあげる胸の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:03.75,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:13.88,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もし君が旅人になったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:20.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どれくらい君を待てるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:25.99,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}季節が変わるそのたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.85,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}記憶が薄らぐことがあっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:39.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かをこんなふうに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:47.61,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心いっぱいで愛せないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:56.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}守りたい　大切な君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:02.60,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつだって二人は独りじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:09.76,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この胸が　壊れそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:16.34,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}触れてほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.19,0:24:26.08,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}切なくて　もどかしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:32.37,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帰れない　このまま歩いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:39.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}指先に　感じている
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:46.52,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:22:01.69,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你方才说出的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:08.27,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}轻轻落在我的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:13.58,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}缄口不语也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:20.46,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖了紧紧相连的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:27.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}话语即是话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:35.71,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一半心意无法传达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:44.13,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}多么伤心 多么焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:50.69,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}晚霞包裹着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.65,0:22:57.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中的思念油然而生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:03.75,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:13.88,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你成为旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:20.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我要把你等到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:25.99,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每当季节更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:32.85,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}记忆都越发稀薄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:39.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为我无法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:47.61,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全心全意地爱一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:56.53,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要守护 珍重的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:24:02.60,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不论何时 两人都不孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:09.76,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我这颗心 即将破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:16.34,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你来抚慰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.19,0:24:26.08,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}多么伤心 多么焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:32.37,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没有回去 愿这样漫步下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:39.53,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我的指尖 感觉到那
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.97,0:24:46.52,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:51.27,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}じゃあまたね　手を振った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:56.56,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}後ろ姿あんなにも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:04.04,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れの人波に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:08.73,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺れながら小さくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:18.27,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがくれた言葉を　ひとつずつ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:24.63,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出し 目を閉じた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:37.46,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せな思いだけ　ここにあるはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:45.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不安になる　どうしてなの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:50.81,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心が震えてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:56.36,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝えたいもっとそう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:02.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}溢れてる　この気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:10.23,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだから　好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:16.37,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}绝対好きだから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:26.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向いて　駆け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:31.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追いかけて行きたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:38.61,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夕暮れの寂しさが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:43.58,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな勇気飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:53.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの笑顏の中に　私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:59.71,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し離れただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷子になったような
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:12.77,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}子供みたい　泣き出しそう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:19.52,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直なら　こんな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:25.34,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}しなくてもすむのになぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:31.11,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}からっぽのあたしだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.05,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.01,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叫んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:44.95,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きだから　好きだから
